data.description: A stunning 2-story home in Porter, TX. This spacious home offers 2,218 sq ft of living space and sits on a 10,274 sq ft lot. With 5 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, it provides ample room.  The master bedroom is conveniently located on the first floor & features a walk-in closet. Upstairs, there's a game room for entertainment. The home is adorned with wood blinds, A a gas fireplace.  The backyard includes a shed for storage. The laundry room features a Dutch door.   Nestled in a fantastic community, residents of this neighborhood enjoy access to a variety of amenities, including a community pool, playground, and basketball court. There are also walking trails for outdoor enthusiasts to enjoy nature.  For families with young children, Crippen Elementary School is conveniently located nearby, ensuring a short commute for students.  Easy access to 99.
